import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1, x2):
    v0 = jnp.subtract(x1, x0)
    v1 = jnp.tanh(x0)
    v2 = jnp.multiply(x1, x2)
    v3 = jnp.subtract(x0, v2)
    v4 = jnp.subtract(v0, x0)
    v5 = jnp.exp(x1)
    v6 = jnp.add(x0, x2)
    v7 = jnp.subtract(v3, v0)
